The paper discusses the training of deep neural networks, specifically CNNs for image recognition, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL) since the techniques used in the paper can be applied to various domains. The paper also mentions the use of transfer learning, which falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
